          "expression": "pleasure_02",
          "text": "...Actually... There's an anime on Sunday mornings called 'Lily Cure' that I...",
          "voiceFile": "talk_anime_secret_002"
        },
        {
          "character": "player",
          "expression": "normal_01",
          "text": "Lily Cure? The one where the girls transform?"
